==細節==
根據PFIF建立的網站可以輕易傳輸，導出數據進行網頁採集[[网页抓取|網頁抓取]]。<ref name="npr"/>   {{link-en|軟件部件|software widget}} 共有兩個按鈕，一個是"我在尋找某人"，另一個是"我有某人的信息"。該部件可以輕易加載在任何一個網站中。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mediapost.com/publications/?fa=Articles.showArticle&art_aid=120792|publisher=Search Insider|title=Haiti on my Mind|author=Derek Gordon|date=2010-01-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100120225112/http://www.mediapost.com/publications/?fa=Articles.showArticle&art_aid=120792|archivedate=2010-01-20|accessdate=2013-04-21}}</ref>

該尋人系統在2011年有幾次誤報。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1366058/Japan-earthquake-tsunami-Sick-death-messages-falsely-inform-families.html?ito=feeds-newsxml|publisher=Daily Mail|title='Sick' messages falsely inform worried British families their relatives are dead after Japanese earthquake|date=March 14, 2011|accessdate=2013-04-21|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020111753/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1366058/Japan-earthquake-tsunami-Sick-death-messages-falsely-inform-families.html?ito=feeds-newsxml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

